# 🚀 Roadmap.sh Clone

A responsive frontend clone of the popular roadmap.sh website, built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Bootstrap**. This project was created to improve my frontend development skills by recreating a modern, responsive, and interactive user interface.

## 📌 Features

- Responsive Navigation Bar
- Custom Dropdown Menus
- Hero Section
- Role-Based Roadmaps
- Skill-Based Roadmaps
- Project Ideas Section
- Best Practices Section
- Guides Section
- Actively Maintained Timeline
- Join the Community Section
- Responsive Footer
- Smooth Hover Effects & Animations
- Mobile Friendly Layout

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Bootstrap 5
- Bootstrap Icons

