## 🎯 Purpose

The purpose of this project was to practice:

- Responsive Web Design
- Modern UI Development
- Bootstrap Layout System
- CSS Flexbox & Grid
- JavaScript DOM Manipulation
- Clean Project Structure

## 🚀 Getting Started

1. Clone the repository

```bash
https://github.com/umerfarooq0320/Roadmap.sh-clone.git
```

2. Open the project folder

```bash
cd roadmap-sh-clone
```

3. Open `index.html` in your browser or use **Live Server**.

## 📌 Note

This project is created **for educational and learning purposes only**. It is a frontend practice project inspired by the original roadmap.sh website and is not affiliated with or endorsed by roadmap.sh.

